<br>
&quot;12.5% base + .5% per lvl past lvl 1, so a base chance of 37.5% chance to DW per round if you put no points into it. Spec points bumps it by .5% per point, and each RA level of Duelist reflexes bumps it 3%.<br>
<br>
For example, lets take my char - <br>
<br>
Base 37.5%<br>
+items/RR = +16 = 8%<br>
Celtic Dual skill of 19 = 9.5%<br>
Dualist lvl 2 = 6%<br>
<br>
Total chance for me to swing both hands in a round:<br>
61%<br>
<br>
Lucke Fabulous&quot;<br>
<br>
