<br>
Generally, the spread is about 60% for singles, 20% for doubles, 12% for triples, and 8% for quads.  It takes a very, very large sample of attacks to demonstrate the difference between 25 HTH and 50 HTH on these numbers.<br>
<br>
Duelists' Reflexes, from tests, seems to only affect the chance to single or dual hit, leaving the triple and quad numbers untouched.  I'm waiting on confirmation that this is the way it's meant to be.<br>
